snippet.title: Aliens: Colonial Marines - Movie Map Pack
snippet.description:
You'll be awesome for hitting that Like button and subscribing, guys.

This is the new Movie Map Pack for Aliens: Colonial Marines.  The pack features 4 new multiplayer maps:

Survivor mode: Nostromo
Escape mode: Exodus
Team Deathmatch mode: Fury 161 and Processor

Wishing you all the best.

PSN: SK4SF
